# Copy to `.dev.vars` for `wrangler dev`. Real values live in Cloudflare
# (set with `wrangler secret put` or the dashboard) and are NEVER committed.

# Comma-separated list of origins allowed to call /api/subscribe.
# Example for production: https://example.pages.dev,https://sapphireservers.com
ALLOWED_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
